24:21.060 --> 24:23.620
Yeah, well,
I got a promotion myself.

24:23.762 --> 24:24.991
Yeah.

24:25.130 --> 24:26.427
To price marker, right?

24:26.565 --> 24:27.965
Yeah, how'd you know that?

24:28.100 --> 24:32.298
Not too many hands sell
three for 29 cents.

24:33.672 --> 24:35.470
Yeah, well, not without
the coupons.

24:35.607 --> 24:36.973
Ha, just get me a burger.

24:37.109 --> 24:38.372
Yes, sir, sit right here.

24:38.510 --> 24:39.534
Uh, sure.

24:39.678 --> 24:41.169
I'll have this cleaned up
right away.

24:41.313 --> 24:43.338
- It's tough getting good help
today. -Mm.

24:43.482 --> 24:44.916
You, get out here!

24:45.050 --> 24:46.541
We got dirty tables!

24:46.685 --> 24:48.813
Shake a leg!

24:48.954 --> 24:50.445
Burger to stay!

